00020000                            ; ROM range: 0x020000-0x03FFFF
00020000                            ; Bank-local ownership skeleton for the first fully banked mid-ROM region.
00020000                            ; This bank still needs deeper code/text/table recovery, but the upstream quiz slice at
00020000                            ; 0x021360-0x02171F, the adjacent name/text region at 0x021720-0x02245F, the first
00020000                            ; post-dictionary descriptor/index island at 0x022460-0x022C5F, and a later sentinel-
00020000                            ; delimited word-record band at 0x023AB6-0x024537 are now split into ROM-order modules
00020000                            ; so the bank is no longer a single opaque slice.
00020000                            
00020000                            Bank020000:
